---
import founderImage from "../assets/founder-1.png";
---

<section class="bg-[#FAF7F2] py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-14 px-5 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[0.88fr_1.12fr] lg:gap-16">
    <img
      src={founderImage.src}
      alt="A Children First team member reflecting on volunteer impact"
      class="h-[500px] w-full rounded-[2rem] object-cover sm:h-[680px] lg:rounded-[3rem]"
    />

    <div>
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#D97706] sm:text-sm">
        Volunteer Voices
      </p>

      <blockquote class="mt-7">
        <p class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#1F2937] sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
          &ldquo;The smallest act of attention can become the moment a child starts believing they matter.&rdquo;
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-[#1F2937]/70 md:text-xl md:leading-9">
        Our volunteers bring more than time. They bring consistency, warmth and the everyday encouragement that helps children feel less alone in their journey.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
